renderArea

void renderArea(android.graphics.Paint paint,
                int level)
Renders an area with the given parameters.

Parameters:
paint - the paint to be used for rendering the area.
level - the drawing level on which the area should be rendered.

void renderAreaCaption(String caption,
                       float verticalOffset,
                       android.graphics.Paint paint,
                       android.graphics.Paint stroke)
Renders an area caption with the given text.

Parameters:
caption - the text to be rendered.
verticalOffset - the vertical offset of the caption.
paint - the paint to be used for rendering the text.
stroke - an optional paint for the text casing (may be null).
